review: Overall good experience with doctor. Dr. lanjot is incredibly knowledgeable and took the time to answer all my questions. Highly recommend.
Very nice and polite doctor listened to the patient very patiently had a great experience there will recommend to everyone

I had a very good experience. Dr. Tanjot Kaur gave me a very patient hearing without being in any hurry. 
She could quickly diagnose the problem and prescribed medication and asked us to visit after a month. I have a lot of improvement. Highly recommended a doctor *** ** *** **** ************* ** ******

Visited her twice- on 8th August 2022 and today for the health issues of my wife. She is patient,well behaved,courteous and comforting. She hears the patient and also the person accompanying the patient and let them complete their part of story. She  prescribes only those medicines that are required. In addition she examines the patient thoroughly. I give her 10 out of 10.
